00:19:15,438 --> 00:19:19,947
They made warp strands like, and made the gaps this size.

169
00:19:23,561 --> 00:19:29,430
I made grass mats for kayaks.

170
00:19:30,500 --> 00:19:39,250
Then my mother watched and said to me, "Look, twist them this way like this."

171
00:19:40,419 --> 00:19:45,388
Then when I started doing that, they started becoming like this.

172
00:19:45,484 --> 00:19:55,900
You see, the small grass mats for kayaks I made are inland in Mikelnguut Elitnaurviat, and my name is there, Elena Charles.

