191
00:21:31,331 --> 00:21:36,256
But their floors had holes.

192
00:21:36,580 --> 00:21:39,916
And the fish in them wouldn’t spoil.

193
00:21:40,367 --> 00:21:44,702
And the frozen fish inside the fish bags would be very good.

194
